snippet.title: Skyward Sword HD Randomizer Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab the latest release here: https://github.com/mint-choc-chip-skyblade/sshd-rando/releases

Join the discord server early: https://discord.gg/nNbpfH5jyG

This project has been in the works for about 10 months and is being developed by Covenesme, gymnast86, Nino, TBPixel, and YourAverageLink.

This trailer was made by the project lead CovenEsme. For dumb reasons, she can't post external links in youtube descriptions which is why the trailer was instead uploaded to my channel.
